  <intervention>
    <intervention_type>Drug</intervention_type>
    <intervention_name>PTX-200</intervention_name>
    <description>During the Phase I study, increasing dose levels of PTX-200 will be administered as an intravenous infusion on days 1, 8 and 15 of each cycle. Triciribine will be infused over 1 hour on days 1, 8, and 15 of each 21 day cycle. The initial dose level will be 25 mg/m2 and each dose level will be increased by 10 mg/m2 to a maximum dose of 55 mg/m2</description>
